Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳\N{\rEN}Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳\N{\rEN}Eileen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要I-37那张表格\N{\rEN}I need form I-37.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 调任书吗 - 不是\N{\rEN}- Transfer form? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,入职的那张 I-37\N{\rEN}Intake. I-37.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你有在听吗\N{\rEN}Aren't you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,她真没用\N{\rEN}She is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还需要弗莱医生的签字\N{\rEN}Dr. Frye still needs to sign it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他可能在办公室里睡着了\N{\rEN}He's probably asleep in his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,至少你能去叫醒弗莱医生吧\N{\rEN}Maybe you could go wake up Dr. Frye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在他耳边轻轻吹口气\N{\rEN}Blow softly in his ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他就喜欢这样\N{\rEN}He loves that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,让她一个人待会儿吧\N{\rEN}Leave Eileen alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,她看起来很累\N{\rEN}She's tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是这样吗\N{\rEN}Oh, is that what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:05:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是每个月的那个日子来了\N{\rEN}I thought maybe it was that time of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我是这样的\N{\rEN}At least I have a time of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 你知道吗 亲爱的\N{\rEN}Oh, yeah. You know something, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这不会永远持续下去的 很快你就跟我们一样老了\N{\rEN}It won't last forever. You'll be old like us soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,请纳尔逊夫人到拜访区\N{\rEN}Mrs. Nelson to the visiting area, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Nelson to the visiting area.\N{\rEN}请纳尔逊夫人到拜访区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会和任何人打架 我跟你说了\N{\rEN}I'm not gonna fight with anybody. I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,米奇怎么样\N{\rEN}How's Mickey doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经在努力变好了\N{\rEN}I'm trying to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下 坐下 坐下\N{\rEN}Sit down. Sit down. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我的错...\N{\rEN}Well, it's not my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是下次再来吧\N{\rEN}Maybe I'll see you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管我们都会怀念这个老家伙\N{\rEN}As much as we're gonna miss the old dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我还是希望下周一大家能热情欢迎\N{\rEN}I hope you'll all be welcoming
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,弗莱医生的继任者\N{\rEN}to Dr. Frye's replacement on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一位优秀的年轻医生\N{\rEN}A fine, fine young doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,希望男孩们都能认真对待她\N{\rEN}Yes, well, let's hope the boys take her seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我会的\N{\rEN}I'll take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\rEN}Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你会带上你的胰岛素\N{\rEN}I think you will be taking your insulin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,还有退休金\N{\rEN}and your retirement package.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这两样就够了吧\N{\rEN}That'll be enough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEN}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我会怀念你们的\N{\rEN}I'll really miss all the fun around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为弗莱医生鼓掌\N{\rEN}Let's hear it for Dr. Frye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,干杯\N{\rEN}Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,最近好多人都点安妮酒啊\N{\rEN}I see a lot of Anne these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 外面有很多伤心人\N{\rEN}Yeah, a lot of broken hearts out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 亲爱的\N{\rEN}Hey, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rEN}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸怎么样了\N{\rEN}How's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的\N{\rEN}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,还是我来吧\N{\rEN}You know what? Let me get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEN}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...你他妈的赶紧闭嘴吧\N{\rEN}...want you to go inside and shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你才…你才闭嘴\N{\rEN}You shut... you shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,滚蛋 住口 你闭嘴\N{\rEN}Fuck off! Shut up! You shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 臭酒鬼 我会...\N{\rEN}Fucking booze bag! Oh, I'll do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我还要再喝一杯  - 嘿 你还好吗\N{\rEN}- I'm gonna have a drink. - You all right there, chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以滚了\N{\rEN}You can fuck right off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因为隔壁那个该死的路德教徒 不是我\N{\rEN}Goddamn Lutherans next door are the problem, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人说你 我们只是想确保\N{\rEN}Nobody's complaining. We just want to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你能安然无恙地到家\N{\rEN}you're getting home safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没人吗 啊\N{\rEN}Nobody's complaining?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 爸爸  - 狗屁安然无恙\N{\rEN}- Dad. - Safe and sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我还能出什么事儿吗\N{\rEN}Why wouldn't I be safe and sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,爸\N{\rEN}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,整个社区的安全我都有责任\N{\rEN}I keep the whole fucking neighborhood safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你知道个屁 - 爸爸\N{\rEN}- What do you know? - Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,艾...艾琳 进去吧\N{\rEN}E-Eileen, go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好啊 爸爸 你看着我 - 进去吧\N{\rEN}- Okay. Dad, look to me. - Go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 拜托了\N{\rEN}Come on. Please. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你这是在闹事\N{\rEN}Hey! You're causing a scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 艾琳 没有人会别无所图地跟你在一起\N{\rEN}Trust me, Eileen. Nobody wants nothing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 - 哇\N{\rEN}- Okay. - Mwah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快点 进去  - 哇\N{\rEN}- Come on. Go inside. - Mwah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那些该死的路德教徒就在那里\N{\rEN}Goddamn Lutherans right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈一直讨厌那些人\N{\rEN}Your mother always hated those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 天哪 我们快进去吧  - 他们可以滚了 就这么定了\N{\rEN}- Gosh, let's go inside. - They can fuck off. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能到处去管别人 爸爸\N{\rEN}You can't go around policing people, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谁说的 你知道是哪个人说的吗\N{\rEN}Who says? You know who that guy was?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都在掌控之中 长官\N{\rEN}We got it all under control, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用这么紧张\N{\rEN}You can take it easy. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还别紧张 你他妈的敢松懈吗\N{\rEN}Take it easy? Y-You fuckin' take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经不是警察了\N{\rEN}You're not a cop anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊  你说的对\N{\rEN}Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想退休 都是他们干的\N{\rEN}I didn't want to retire. They made me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是因为我太优秀了\N{\rEN}'cause I was too goddamn good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我得回去了\N{\rEN}Look, I gotta get back to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,给我倒杯喝的\N{\rEN}Pour me a drink. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧 巴克\N{\rEN}Get back to the station, Buck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,把喝的给我\N{\rEN}Give me my drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你还需要什么 就给我们打电话\N{\rEN}Just give us a call if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐\N{\rEN}Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你过来 那是什么味道\N{\rEN}Hey, come here. What's that smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你有踩到什么东西吗\N{\rEN}Did you step in something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 为什么这么问 你是闻到什么味道了吗\N{\rEN}No. Why? What do you smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 像是踩到了路边被撞死的动物\N{\rEN}I don't know. Roadkill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你得保持点儿距离\N{\rEN}Maybe you should keep your distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了\N{\rEN}Yeah, I'll keep my distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈在搞什么 把我的鞋给我穿回去\N{\rEN}The fuck you doing? Put my fucking shoes back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你是不是得对我好点儿\N{\rEN}But maybe you should be nicer to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没人能忍受得了你这样\N{\rEN}No one else is gonna put up with your shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就走吧 我还有乔·安妮呢\N{\rEN}Go then, 'cause I got Joanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她才不会让家里变成这样\N{\rEN}She wouldn't keep a place looking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你妹妹是个真正的女人\N{\rEN}She's a real woman, your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,味道也不像你\N{\rEN}And she smells like a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,她知道怎么持家\N{\rEN}She knows how to keep a house!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但是她不住在这里 而且她已经结婚了\N{\rEN}And she doesn't live here, and she's married!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 她也不会在这里蹭吃蹭喝\N{\rEN}Yeah, 'cause she's not a hanger-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么不说她都不想跟你说话\N{\rEN}And she doesn't want to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 那是因为她有自己的生活\N{\rEN}Yeah, sure, 'cause she's made a life of her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,也有自己的事情要忙\N{\rEN}She's made something of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓了 爸爸\N{\rEN}Whatever, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好好生活吧 艾琳 别这么混下去了\N{\rEN}Get a life, Eileen. Get a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\rEN}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,滚吧\N{\rEN}Fuck it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 听着\N{\rEN}All right, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都知道了 今年\N{\rEN}As you know, in the new year,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要接受审查\N{\rEN}we will be up for state review.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们要加强我们的规程管理\N{\rEN}So we're gonna be tightening our procedures
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,同时基于一些不错的想法实施新的计划\N{\rEN}and implementing new strategies based on some big, new ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,说到这里 我左边的这位新来的年轻的女士\N{\rEN}And on that note, this new young lady to my left,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞贝卡·圣约翰\N{\rEN}Dr. Miss Rebecca St. John,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们新来的监狱心理学家\N{\rEN}is our new prison psychologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她刚在拉德克利夫读完博士学位\N{\rEN}She's just finished her doctorate at Radcliffe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哈佛\N{\rEN}Harvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 哈佛\N{\rEN}Ah. Harvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能不是哈佛人\N{\rEN}We may not be Harvard people,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但我觉得我们可以跟上她的步伐\N{\rEN}but I think we can keep up with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,同时也希望她还有我们大家\N{\rEN}and hopefully she can keep up with us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,都能保持同样的节奏\N{\rEN}as we keep up with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,她可能看起来很讨人喜欢 但我向你们保证\N{\rEN}She may be easy on the eyes, but I assure you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,她同时也非常聪明\N{\rEN}she is very smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们 我希望你们带圣约翰小姐四处看看…\N{\rEN}Ladies, I hope you show Miss St. John around...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这得多少钱\N{\rEN}Say, how much for a glazed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是免费的\N{\rEN}They're free.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,开玩笑啦\N{\rEN}I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我是瑞贝卡\N{\rEN}I'm Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rEN}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 梳妆的地方在哪里呢\N{\rEN}Say, where can a girl get freshened up around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我带你去\N{\rEN}I can show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢啦\N{\rEN}Sure. Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以帮你拿着夹克\N{\rEN}Can I take your jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,太贴心了 谢谢\N{\rEN}Aren't you sweet? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这边\N{\rEN}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你有说过自己的名字吗\N{\rEN}I don't think I caught your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳\N{\rEN}Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 早 - 早\N{\rEN}- Morning. - Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你是从哪儿来的\N{\rEN}Where you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEN}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 纽约\N{\rEN}Oh, I'm from New York originally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,曼哈顿\N{\rEN}Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我受不了剑桥 那里的人太保守了\N{\rEN}Couldn't stand Cambridge. Way too uptight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,倒是有几个有意思的人\N{\rEN}Well, there were a couple of interesting people,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我还是觉得自己需要休息休息\N{\rEN}but, no, I needed a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,呼吸点儿新鲜的空气\N{\rEN}Get some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢海滩\N{\rEN}And I love the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rEN}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,32...\N{\rEN}32...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,24...\N{\rEN}24...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...34\N{\rEN}...34.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的三围\N{\rEN}Practically my measurements.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 有些女性会觉得自己的身材\N{\rEN}You know, some women think their figures
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,才是唯一重要的事情\N{\rEN}are the only thing that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说 我觉得这有点可悲\N{\rEN}Honestly, I think that's kind of pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,完全同意\N{\rEN}I completely agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我姐姐就是这样 而且她也没有很时髦\N{\rEN}My sister's like that, and she's not very smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那很好 这样你和我\N{\rEN}Mm, good. Then you and I
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,除了这些就有更好的趣事儿可以聊了\N{\rEN}have better things to discuss than our figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然都不是些主流的话题\N{\rEN}Although that isn't the popular opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你说呢\N{\rEN}wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不在乎流行什么呢\N{\rEN}I don't care what's popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 看看你\N{\rEN}Well, look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,活脱脱一个日常的凯瑟琳·赫本\N{\rEN}A regular Katharine Hepburn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很少见到这么有进取心的年轻的女孩子\N{\rEN}Rare to meet a young woman with so much gumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是这样的\N{\rEN}I'm like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不在乎人们的想法\N{\rEN}I don't give a rat's ass what people think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可能会更害怕你\N{\rEN}They're probably scared of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我吗\N{\rEN}Moi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 回头见\N{\rEN}All right. See you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,每年\N{\rEN}Every year,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都会举行这次特别的集会\N{\rEN}we hold this special assembly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,来庆祝我主耶稣基督的诞生\N{\rEN}to celebrate the birth of Our Lord Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但是每一年 你们这些混蛋里的某个人\N{\rEN}And every year, one of you sick bastards
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,都会给我搞砸\N{\rEN}ruins it for the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这种事情今年就不会再发生了\N{\rEN}Well, you've disrespected Christmas for the last time
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因为今年 你们都得闭上嘴\N{\rEN}because this year, you're gonna sit on your hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好好坐着\N{\rEN}you're gonna zip your lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我看到你们中间有人闹事的话\N{\rEN}If I see any of you biting, kicking, screaming, pushing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是什么\N{\rEN}pulling hair, laughing, moaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,或者让我听到任何一句任性的评论\N{\rEN}or I hear one wayward comment,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,都会直接被我关禁闭\N{\rEN}you're going straight to the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 话不多说\N{\rEN}And now, without further ado,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.88,0:15:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我很荣幸向橄榄山的人们表达感谢\N{\rEN}it is my honor to thank the people from Mount Olive
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,今年多亏了他们的帮助…\N{\rEN}who helped me direct the pageant again this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 耶 橄榄山 - 才能把这出表演带给你们\N{\rEN}- Yay, Mount Olive. - and present to you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎欣赏 监狱里的圣诞节\N{\rEN}"Christmas in Prison."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我要在圣诞节杀个人\N{\rEN}I'm gonna kill someone on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,住口\N{\rEN}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我该怎么办\N{\rEN}Oh, what am I to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,三年的牢狱\N{\rEN}Sentenced for three years to sit indoors
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,跟那些和我有一样的信仰的男孩儿们在一起 真的是太糟了\N{\rEN}among boys of my same creed, plain bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不过现在有这么多时间来策划\N{\rEN}So much time to plot
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,等我出去之后做什么坏事儿\N{\rEN}what evildoings I'll undertake as soon as I get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃蛋糕吗 你这个胖子\N{\rEN}You want some cake, you fatty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,或者我可以读本书\N{\rEN}In the meantime, I suppose I could read a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你会读吗 混蛋\N{\rEN}You can't read, motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈的莎士比亚就在下面坐着呢\N{\rEN}Fucking Shakespeare up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在很烦躁\N{\rEN}I'm scrappy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真理之书\N{\rEN}Book of truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 看看麦卡利斯特\N{\rEN}Oh, look at McAllister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的是麦卡利斯特\N{\rEN}Fucking McAllister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 挺不错的啊\N{\rEN}Hey, nice rack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我...我好累\N{\rEN}Well, I'm-I'm pretty tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以在外面的谷仓里休息吗\N{\rEN}Can we rest in that barn over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,比付钱住旅馆更好\N{\rEN}Better than paying for a motel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是最棒的 约瑟夫\N{\rEN}You're the best, Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你带我们来参加人口普查\N{\rEN}Thank you for taking us here to be counted in the census.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的狗屎\N{\rEN}Fuck this shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,警卫 等等\N{\rEN}Guard! Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 抓住他\N{\rEN}Wait. Wait, wait. Hey, grab him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,后退\N{\rEN}Move back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,都坐下\N{\rEN}All you guys sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的坐下\N{\rEN}Sit the fuck down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 鲍勃\N{\rEN}Hey, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 亲爱的\N{\rEN}Hey, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这个还有一包幸运牌香烟\N{\rEN}This and a pack of Luckies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真是幸运的一天 是吧\N{\rEN}Oh! It's a lucky day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 最幸运的一天\N{\rEN}Yeah, the luckiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 那些香烟很棒\N{\rEN}Yup. Cigarettes are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,别烧着自己了\N{\rEN}Don't light yourself on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你心情挺不错的 怎么了\N{\rEN}You're in a good mood, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么 爸爸\N{\rEN}Nothing's wrong, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你叼着烟看起来挺蠢的\N{\rEN}You look funny with that thing in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天怎么样啊 爸爸\N{\rEN}How was your day, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我吗\N{\rEN}How was my day?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\rEN}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一天又一天的\N{\rEN}It was a day, just another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么区别\N{\rEN}What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天过得挺充实的\N{\rEN}My day was a doozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.28,0:18:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\rEN}Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞节庆典上有人打起来了\N{\rEN}A big fight broke out at the Christmas pageant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有个孩子骨折了\N{\rEN}Kid got his collarbone broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我得为典狱长做这些文书工作\N{\rEN}and I had to do all this paperwork for the warden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,别把烟灰抖在地上 会发粘\N{\rEN}Don't ash on the floor, it's tacky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,反正...\N{\rEN}Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是个永远都不会忘记的一天\N{\rEN}It was one of those days you never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 我想想看\N{\rEN}Oh, yeah? Days I'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那些我永远都不会忘记的日子\N{\rEN}Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,1944 年 12 月 16 日\N{\rEN}December 16, 1944,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次把死人的头抱在腿上\N{\rEN}first time I ever held a dead man's head in my lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真是浪费啊\N{\rEN}What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,外面20度 正在下雪\N{\rEN}20 degrees outside and snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这里一样\N{\rEN}Just like it is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道自己为什么又回到了这个地方\N{\rEN}Don't know why I ever came back to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是因为你有老婆和两个孩子\N{\rEN}Maybe because you had a wife and two kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,或许吧\N{\rEN}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢海滩\N{\rEN}I love the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 真为你高兴\N{\rEN}Oh, yeah? Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那些战争已经毁了我对海滩的好感\N{\rEN}War kind of ruined beaches for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么\N{\rEN}So what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那个波尔克小子怎么样 他招了吗\N{\rEN}How's that Polk kid? He talked yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEN}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,波尔克\N{\rEN}Polk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那个刺伤父亲的孩子...\N{\rEN}The kid who stabbed his father...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...他爸怎么说也算是个好警察\N{\rEN}...who was a good cop, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什么样的孩子会想着像这样杀死自己的父亲呢\N{\rEN}What kind of kid thinks of killing his father like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,趁他睡着的时候捅他一刀……\N{\rEN}Stab him in his sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还是在他母亲面前\N{\rEN}in front of his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他就那么坐下了\N{\rEN}Then he just sits down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也不否认\N{\rEN}Never denies it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,整个审判过程中一句话也不说\N{\rEN}Never says a word the whole trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,神经病一样\N{\rEN}Psychopathic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然不用担心你\N{\rEN}Course I wouldn't have to worry about you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,会做那样的事 我需要担心吗\N{\rEN}doing something like that, now, would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个女孩\N{\rEN}'Cause you're a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我都想象不出来你拿着刀的样子\N{\rEN}Can't imagine you with a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那你能想象出来我拿着枪吗\N{\rEN}Can you imagine me with a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能看见...\N{\rEN}Yeah, I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也许有一天...\N{\rEN}One day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,当你受够了 感觉 呃...\N{\rEN}when you've had enough and you feel like, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,想要悄悄溜走\N{\rEN}ducking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,也可能是我死了之后\N{\rEN}Maybe when I'm dead and gone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你身边什么人也没有 而且是永远\N{\rEN}and you got nobody and you never will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以想象到那个\N{\rEN}I could imagine that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不会 对吗\N{\rEN}But you wouldn't, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你太优秀了\N{\rEN}'Cause you're too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 给我一根香烟\N{\rEN}Say, give me one of those cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你抽的是什么 老金吗\N{\rEN}What have you got, Old Gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\rEN}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我更喜欢那个\N{\rEN}I like Old Gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:20:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rEN}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,诶\N{\rEN}Oopsie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.14,0:22:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,需要帮忙吗\N{\rEN}Do you need any help?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.62,0:22:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,额 不用 没啥事儿\N{\rEN}Uh, no, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就是没拿稳东西\N{\rEN}Just butterfingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你真应该看看我\N{\rEN}You should see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个十足的笨蛋\N{\rEN}I'm a total klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是这个\N{\rEN}Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.94,0:22:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,李·波尔克\N{\rEN}Lee Polk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.29,0:22:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不是你每天都能看到的\N{\rEN}That's not something you see every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 真的影响很不好\N{\rEN}Yeah, it's pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 睡前读物吗\N{\rEN}Bedtime reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 就是在归档\N{\rEN}I was just doing some filing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.13,0:22:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为昨天的那场好戏吗\N{\rEN}That's some show yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.05,0:22:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们每年都会那样\N{\rEN}They do it every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.40,0:22:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这是残酷且不寻常的惩罚\N{\rEN}I'd call that cruel and unusual punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.37,0:22:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我一般不抽烟\N{\rEN}Sorry. I don't usually smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.98,0:22:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,确实是个令人讨厌的习惯\N{\rEN}It's a nasty habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.59,0:22:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才喜欢它\N{\rEN}That's why I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:22:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然看上去不太像是个淑女就是了\N{\rEN}Not very becoming of a lady, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.72,0:22:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,会让牙齿变黄\N{\rEN}Turns your teeth yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.85,0:23:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了没\N{\rEN}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.55,0:23:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因为香烟和咖啡\N{\rEN}That's cigarettes and coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.64,0:23:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还有红酒\N{\rEN}And red wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.16,0:23:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你的牙齿很完美\N{\rEN}No, your teeth are perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喝咖啡\N{\rEN}I don't drink coffee,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.17,0:23:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我的牙齿应该没什么问题的 但是…\N{\rEN}so my teeth should be fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.48,0:23:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,…它们也都蛀了\N{\rEN}...they're all rotted
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.92,0:23:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我非常喜欢甜食\N{\rEN}due to my extreme propensity for sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.27,0:23:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哈 喜欢吃甜食吗\N{\rEN}A propensity for sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你的生活给不了你那些甜分吗\N{\rEN}You don't get enough sweetness in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.14,0:23:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是会吃很多糖果\N{\rEN}I just eat a lot of candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.06,0:23:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 我可看不出来\N{\rEN}Mm. I wouldn't know it to look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.06,0:23:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你还蛮较小的\N{\rEN}You're so petite.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 身高也有它的优势\N{\rEN}Being tall has its advantages, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但大多数男人对我来说都太矮了\N{\rEN}but most men are just too short for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.80,0:23:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有注意到 还是说都是我想象的\N{\rEN}Have you noticed, or am I imagining things,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的男人越来越矮了\N{\rEN}that men these days are getting shorter and shorter,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.42,0:23:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,又秃又胖\N{\rEN}balder, and fatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.81,0:23:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可是这里的男人可都是些小男孩\N{\rEN}All the men around here are little boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.43,0:23:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真幽默\N{\rEN}You're funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的是外面的男人\N{\rEN}I meant outside this prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.69,0:23:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然你说得对\N{\rEN}Although you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.73,0:23:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,警卫们 监狱长\N{\rEN}The guards, the warden,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:23:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,都没什么看头\N{\rEN}they're not much to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.65,0:23:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你真应该去看看弗莱医生\N{\rEN}You should have seen Dr. Frye.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.74,0:24:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他的确是非常难看了\N{\rEN}He was really pretty nasty looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.48,0:24:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一点儿也不惊讶\N{\rEN}That doesn't surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.27,0:24:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我的办公室真的让人很不适应\N{\rEN}My office isn't very becoming,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.44,0:24:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,到处都是脏皮革的味道\N{\rEN}and it all smells of dirty leather.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.36,0:24:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始想知道里面都发生过什么了\N{\rEN}I'm beginning to wonder what went on in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.10,0:24:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么好事儿就是了\N{\rEN}Nothing good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.36,0:24:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,别误会 我也从来没进去过\N{\rEN}I mean, I never actually been in that office.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.19,0:24:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 那你应该找个时间过来坐坐\N{\rEN}Oh. Well, you should come by sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.98,0:24:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果门关着的话\N{\rEN}Although if the door's closed,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.15,0:24:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那就说明我正在跟这里的某个男孩儿谈话\N{\rEN}that means I'm with one of the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.42,0:24:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEN}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.85,0:24:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你从来都没害怕过吗\N{\rEN}Aren't you ever scared
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.38,0:24:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他们独处一室\N{\rEN}being alone in there with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.60,0:24:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么好怕的\N{\rEN}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.69,0:24:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有时间就来找我 好吗\N{\rEN}Come by, and see me sometime, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.43,0:24:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 如果你听到我在尖叫的话\N{\rEN}Although, you know, if you hear me screaming in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.21,0:24:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,别犹豫 马上踹开门来救我\N{\rEN}feel free to kick down the door and rescue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.04,0:24:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEN}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.39,0:24:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是开玩笑 亲爱的\N{\rEN}I'm just kidding, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.48,0:24:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有警报器呢\N{\rEN}There's a buzzer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.14,0:25:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来见伦纳德·波尔克的\N{\rEN}I'm here to see Leonard Polk.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.41,0:25:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮·波尔克.\N{\rEN}Anne Polk.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.37,0:25:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,登记表上没有你的名字\N{\rEN}You're not on the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.81,0:25:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是后补的吗\N{\rEN}Are you a late addition?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.77,0:25:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是有人通知我的\N{\rEN}I-I was called.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.25,0:26:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不懂 反正我就来了\N{\rEN}I don't know, I-I'm here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.38,0:26:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那你需要填一张表格\N{\rEN}Well, you need to fill out a form.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.26,0:26:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是邓洛普局长的孩子吗\N{\rEN}Aren't you Chief Dunlop's kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.74,0:26:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEN}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.00,0:26:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我说呢\N{\rEN}I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.00,0:26:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,波尔克夫人 我是圣约翰医生\N{\rEN}Mrs. Polk? I'm Dr. St. John.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.57,0:26:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们讲过电话的 很高兴你来了\N{\rEN}We spoke on the phone. Thank you so much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.88,0:26:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 这就算了\N{\rEN}Oh, no need to bother with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.01,0:26:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道你是谁\N{\rEN}We all know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.49,0:26:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳 你能帮我们开下门吗\N{\rEN}Eileen, would you help us with the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.41,0:26:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.76,0:26:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这边来\N{\rEN}It's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.54,0:26:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘记外套了\N{\rEN}Take your coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.89,0:26:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,请\N{\rEN}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.24,0:26:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 艾琳\N{\rEN}Thank you, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.46,0:26:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,您先请\N{\rEN}After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.96,0:27:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要这样对我\N{\rEN}Why are you doing this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.28,0:27:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\rEN}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.37,0:27:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你有话要对我说吗\N{\rEN}You got something to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.65,0:27:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,让我出去\N{\rEN}Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.82,0:27:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,让我出去 让我出去\N{\rEN}Let me out! Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.09,0:27:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,让我出去\N{\rEN}Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.26,0:27:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你们想怎么处置他都行\N{\rEN}Y-You do... y'all do what you want with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.96,0:27:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,连自己的母亲都不肯说吗\N{\rEN}Won't even talk to his own mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.18,0:27:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直是个令人讨厌的孩子\N{\rEN}He's always been a nasty boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.18,0:27:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,又脏又坏的小子\N{\rEN}A filthy, nasty boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.97,0:27:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我得锁起来了\N{\rEN}I need to lock up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.76,0:27:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,探视时间实际上已经过了20多分钟了\N{\rEN}Visitation hours were actually over 20 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.72,0:27:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我明白了\N{\rEN}Oh, I-I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.85,0:28:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你想在我办公室继续聊吗\N{\rEN}Would you like to keep talking in my office?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.38,0:28:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们走吧 - 转身\N{\rEN}- Let's go. - Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.21,0:28:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了 没必要\N{\rEN}Oh, no. That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.55,0:28:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我需要给他戴上手铐 - 不用\N{\rEN}- I need to cuff him. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.26,0:28:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 李 没关系的\N{\rEN}Don't worry, Lee. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.27,0:28:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么没必要\N{\rEN}That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.01,0:28:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样 她才是医生\N{\rEN}Don't do that. She's a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.92,0:28:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我看她才是需要个医生\N{\rEN}I think she needs a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.19,0:28:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子杀了一名警察\N{\rEN}That kid killed a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.23,0:28:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他杀了他的父亲\N{\rEN}He killed his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.19,0:28:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那还是有区别的\N{\rEN}There's a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.54,0:28:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 真的抱歉 我去看看是谁\N{\rEN}Oh, I'm so sorry. Let me see who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.24,0:28:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 艾琳啊\N{\rEN}Oh, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.20,0:28:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了嘛\N{\rEN}Um, can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.73,0:28:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘记带笔记本了\N{\rEN}You forgot your notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.29,0:28:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 非常感谢你\N{\rEN}Oh, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.95,0:28:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实需要它\N{\rEN}I actually need this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.25,0:28:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有偷偷看过吧\N{\rEN}Um, hope you didn't read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.17,0:28:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 当然没有  - 好好 别紧张\N{\rEN}- No, of course not. - Oh, no,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.69,0:28:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在开玩笑 我的字迹很乱 你肯定也看不懂\N{\rEN}I'm just kidding. It's just chicken scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.57,0:29:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 艾琳\N{\rEN}Wait. Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.22,0:29:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就是问一下\N{\rEN}I don't mean to be forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.75,0:29:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你今天晚上没什么计划的话\N{\rEN}and, um, you probably have other plans already,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.92,0:29:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能去喝一杯吗\N{\rEN}but, um, can I take you to a drink tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.19,0:29:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个该死的镇上 我一个人都不认识\N{\rEN}I don't know anyone in this darn town,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.93,0:29:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果您愿意的话 我很乐意请你喝杯鸡尾酒\N{\rEN}and I'd love to treat you to a cocktail if you're game.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.97,0:29:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好啊  - 可以吗\N{\rEN}- Okay. - Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.67,0:29:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有打乱你的计划吧\N{\rEN}I've twisted your arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.02,0:29:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,镇上最好的马提尼是哪家的\N{\rEN}So, uh, who makes the best martini in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.41,0:29:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也许是奥哈拉的  - 奥哈拉吗\N{\rEN}- Maybe O'Hara's? - O'Hara's.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.33,0:29:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上 这是镇上唯一的酒吧\N{\rEN}It's actually the only bar in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.72,0:29:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不会 这就已经很好了\N{\rEN}No, O'Hara's is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.98,0:29:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上七点见\N{\rEN}See you at 7:00?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.46,0:29:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,叮叮（很热情地要去某个地方的习语） 是这么说的吗\N{\rEN}With bells on? Is that the expression?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.82,0:29:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我知道你被别人♪\N{\rEN}♪ I know you've been hurt♪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.87,0:29:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 伤害了♪\N{\rEN}♪ By someone else♪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.96,0:29:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 从你走路的样子♪\N{\rEN}♪ I can tell by the way♪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.31,0:29:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我就能看出来 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ You carry yourself♪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.40,0:30:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 如果你愿意♪\N{\rEN}♪ But if you let me♪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.41,0:30:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我会这么做♪\N{\rEN}♪ Here's what I'll do♪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.76,0:30:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我会照顾你的♪\N{\rEN}♪ I'll take care of you♪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.02,0:30:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我...我爱过也失去过♪\N{\rEN}♪ I... I've loved and lost♪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.81,0:30:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 和你一样♪\N{\rEN}♪ The same as you♪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.82,0:30:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 所以你看 我知道♪\N{\rEN}♪ So you see, I know♪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.34,0:30:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 你所经历的 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ Just what you've been through ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.56,0:30:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 但如果你允许我♪\N{\rEN}♪ But if you'll let me♪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.31,0:30:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我会这么做♪\N{\rEN}♪ Here's what I'll do♪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.79,0:30:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 哦 我只是要照顾你 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ Oh, I just got to take care of you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.14,0:30:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 你永远不必担心 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ You won't ever have to worry ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.72,0:30:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 你永远不必哭泣♪\N{\rEN}♪ You won't ever have to cry♪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.07,0:31:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 因为我会在你身边 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ For I'll be there beside you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.82,0:31:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 擦干你哭泣的眼睛♪\N{\rEN}♪ To dry your weeping eyes♪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.04,0:31:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 那么 亲爱的♪\N{\rEN}♪ So, darling♪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.83,0:31:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 告诉我♪\N{\rEN}♪ Tell me♪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.14,0:31:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 你愿意吗♪\N{\rEN}♪ That you'll be true♪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.14,0:31:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 不带着一丝疑问...♪\N{\rEN}♪ For there is no doubt...♪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.76,0:31:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 - 哦 艾琳\N{\rEN}- Hi. - Oh, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.93,0:31:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\rEN}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.41,0:31:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,快坐\N{\rEN}Please, please, please, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.63,0:31:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你要什么\N{\rEN}Um, what are you having?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.50,0:31:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,来杯啤酒就行了\N{\rEN}Uh, I'll have a beer, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.94,0:31:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,啤酒啊\N{\rEN}A beer? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.51,0:31:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 艾琳\N{\rEN}Hi, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.81,0:31:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你 亲爱的\N{\rEN}Good to see you, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.90,0:31:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢 亲爱的\N{\rEN}What's next, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.03,0:31:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你真的是\N{\rEN}Um, well... Oh, my stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.47,0:31:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,彻底被冻僵了\N{\rEN}You're absolutely frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.17,0:31:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 请来一杯啤酒 再来点儿威士忌\N{\rEN}Um, one beer, please, and maybe a little whiskey
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.48,0:31:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,暖暖我的女孩儿 怎么样\N{\rEN}to warm up my girl. What say, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.44,0:32:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 你看起来非常迷人\N{\rEN}My, you look very glamorous.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.61,0:32:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只是一件旧衣服\N{\rEN}It's just an old dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.83,0:32:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我来吧\N{\rEN}May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.93,0:32:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢 亲爱的 再来一杯马提尼吗\N{\rEN}How about you, sweetheart? Another martini?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.71,0:32:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 再来一杯 谢谢\N{\rEN}Love one. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.15,0:32:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这次就不要把橄榄弄进去了\N{\rEN}Maybe let's hold the olives this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.72,0:32:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为这个地方很难找\N{\rEN}I thought I'd have a hard time finding this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.67,0:32:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我还是找到了\N{\rEN}but here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.77,0:32:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\rEN}You feeling all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.90,0:32:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我很好\N{\rEN}Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.69,0:32:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 我的车出了点问题\N{\rEN}Uh, there's something wrong with my car,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.34,0:32:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,开车的时候车窗得一直摇下来\N{\rEN}so I have to drive with the windows down,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.30,0:32:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不然车里面就都是烟\N{\rEN}or else it fills with smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.13,0:32:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\rEN}Oh, you're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.48,0:32:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这也太糟糕了\N{\rEN}That sounds absolutely awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.22,0:32:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不能让你老公帮你弄一下吗\N{\rEN}Can't you get your husband to fix that for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.09,0:32:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不 我还没结婚\N{\rEN}Oh, no, I'm not married.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.22,0:32:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直单身\N{\rEN}I've always been single.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.09,0:32:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 如果我身边有什么男人的话\N{\rEN}And when I do have a guy around,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.75,0:32:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那也就是简单玩儿玩儿 不会太久\N{\rEN}it's just for fun, and it's brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.79,0:32:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来不会让什么人在我身边停留太久\N{\rEN}No, I never stay anywhere long with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.10,0:32:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有点像我的权宜之计\N{\rEN}Sort of my modus vivendi
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.32,0:33:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是有点儿病态吧 这得看是什么人\N{\rEN}or my pathology, depending on who I'm talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.72,0:33:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你在摩尔黑德工作了多久了\N{\rEN}How long have you worked at Moorehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.16,0:33:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,三四年了\N{\rEN}Three or four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.20,0:33:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,本来应该只是暂时的\N{\rEN}Uh, it was only supposed to be temporary,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.68,0:33:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,当时是我母亲生病了 所以我才回来待了一阵子\N{\rEN}while I moved back for a bit while my mother was sick,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.90,0:33:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,结果她没有扛过去 所以…\N{\rEN}and then she died, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.30,0:33:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在监狱里工作 时间过得真快\N{\rEN}I've been at the prison, and time's just flown by.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.21,0:33:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\rEN}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.69,0:33:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那可不是个消磨时间的好地方\N{\rEN}Prison is no place for time to fly by.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.96,0:33:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你妈妈的死\N{\rEN}And your mother dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.92,0:33:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这对你而言真的很难 你还这么小\N{\rEN}That's a lot for a young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.96,0:33:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 当时我24岁\N{\rEN}Ah. 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.58,0:33:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你一定很渴望回到那个时候吧 不是吗\N{\rEN}Then you must be eager to get back out there. Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.23,0:33:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我也是个孤儿\N{\rEN}You know, um, I'm an orphan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.76,0:33:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是我叔叔在西部把我养大的\N{\rEN}My uncle raised me out West.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.54,0:33:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个阳光普照的地方\N{\rEN}Where the sun shines.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.20,0:33:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你们是怎么扛过来的\N{\rEN}I don't understand how you all do it here,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.98,0:33:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,一个又一个的冬天\N{\rEN}winter after winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.59,0:33:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说 真的挺毛骨悚然的\N{\rEN}It's positively creepy. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.07,0:33:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我对新英格兰有一种奇怪的依恋\N{\rEN}I'm in a sort of strange love affair with New England.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.34,0:33:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢它 但我也讨厌它\N{\rEN}I love it, but I also hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.38,0:34:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的一切都很真实 不是吗\N{\rEN}Things feel very real here, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.47,0:34:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,希望没有...\N{\rEN}Sort of there's no...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.83,0:34:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...那些不切实际的东西\N{\rEN}...imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.09,0:34:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没有悲伤 也没有那些幻想\N{\rEN}There's no sentimentality or fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.83,0:34:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这里...真的无处可藏了\N{\rEN}There's... there's just nowhere to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.40,0:34:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\rEN}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.23,0:34:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝太多了\N{\rEN}I've had too much to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.15,0:34:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我一喝多就是这样 滔滔不绝的\N{\rEN}I tend to talk when I've had too much to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.36,0:34:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,还行\N{\rEN}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.76,0:34:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,总比话少好\N{\rEN}Mm, it's better than talking too little.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.07,0:34:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天看到李·波尔克了吗\N{\rEN}Did you see Lee Polk today?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.37,0:34:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…\N{\rEN}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.33,0:34:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她有跟你说话吗\N{\rEN}Did she say anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.90,0:34:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,波尔克夫人吗\N{\rEN}Mrs. Polk?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.73,0:34:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她只是心烦意乱\N{\rEN}She was just upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.03,0:34:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那些妈妈们总是这样\N{\rEN}Those mothers are always upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.82,0:34:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得她像个愤怒的女人吗\N{\rEN}Did she seem like an angry woman to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.43,0:34:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 呃...\N{\rEN}I don't know. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.74,0:34:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这里每个人都多少有点儿愤怒\N{\rEN}everyone's kind of angry here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.22,0:34:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是马萨诸塞州\N{\rEN}It's Massachusetts.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.01,0:35:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我在哈佛大学有一位教授\N{\rEN}Well, I had this professor at Harvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.23,0:35:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他很聪明 但也很难搞\N{\rEN}He was brilliant, but very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.23,0:35:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他在囚犯身上做了个实验\N{\rEN}Uh, he did this-- these experiments on prisoners
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.49,0:35:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,用来研究迷幻药对累犯的影响\N{\rEN}studying the effects of psychedelics on recidivism.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.71,0:35:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不同意他的方法\N{\rEN}Now, I don't agree with his methods,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.98,0:35:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么灵丹妙药\N{\rEN}there is no magic pill,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.24,0:35:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...但是如果你能让罪犯们自己吐露出真相 然后感受它\N{\rEN}but... but you can set people free...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.33,0:35:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这样他们就能获得一种类似自由的解脱\N{\rEN}...if you can get them to tell the truth, to feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.42,0:35:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我尝试做的\N{\rEN}That's what I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.99,0:35:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,秘密和谎言\N{\rEN}Secrets and lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.25,0:35:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说 小娃娃…\N{\rEN}I tell you, doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.73,0:35:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,…有些家庭就是这么病态 扭曲\N{\rEN}...some families are so sick, so twisted,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.17,0:35:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一的出路就是有人死掉\N{\rEN}the only way out's for someone to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.87,0:35:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你不这么觉得吗\N{\rEN}Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.78,0:35:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你叫什么名字来着\N{\rEN}Hey! What'd you say your name was?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.48,0:35:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谁 我吗\N{\rEN}Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.70,0:35:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊 我们刚刚还在说\N{\rEN}Ah, yeah. W-We was just saying
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.70,0:35:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来很眼熟\N{\rEN}that you look so familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.18,0:35:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你有演过电影吗 还是别的什么\N{\rEN}Are you in the movies or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.01,0:35:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会 我在男子监狱工作\N{\rEN}Hardly. I work at the boys' prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.66,0:35:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 啊 - 我是艾琳\N{\rEN}- Ah. - I'm Eileen,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.80,0:35:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的朋友瑞贝卡\N{\rEN}and this is my friend, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.97,0:35:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她是一位心理学家\N{\rEN}She's a psychologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.76,0:35:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别害羞 瑞贝卡\N{\rEN}Don't be shy, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.84,0:35:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这些男孩又不会咬人\N{\rEN}These boys won't bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.02,0:35:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想让我们这么做\N{\rEN}Not unless you ask us to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.59,0:36:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这是杰瑞 不用理他\N{\rEN}This is Jerry. You can ignore him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.33,0:36:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经结婚了\N{\rEN}He's married.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.37,0:36:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,杰瑞 你的牙怎么了\N{\rEN}What happened to your teeth, Jerry?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.85,0:36:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟你老婆吵架了吗\N{\rEN}You get into a fight with your old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.73,0:36:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样 他老婆的左拳跟乔·弗雷泽一样\N{\rEN}That's it. His wife's got a left like Joe Frazier.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.68,0:36:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 他…他只是在冰上滑倒了\N{\rEN}Nah, nah. He... he slipped on the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.03,0:36:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我还要去种牙\N{\rEN}I'm gonna grow some new ones, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.12,0:36:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就行了\N{\rEN}Just need a few more of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.69,0:36:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,为杰瑞和他的新牙干杯\N{\rEN}Cheers to that. To Jerry and his new teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.30,0:36:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 你一定非常想要它♪\N{\rEN}♪ You've gotta want it bad♪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.96,0:36:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 渴望已经融入了你的血液 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ If that guy's got into your blood ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.57,0:36:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,要跳舞吗 瑞贝卡\N{\rEN}Feel like dancing, Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.92,0:36:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们俩吗\N{\rEN}With you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.53,0:36:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rEN}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.18,0:36:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 你的真心♪\N{\rEN}♪ The very heart of you♪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.14,0:36:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 让你想要呼吸\N{\rEN}♪ Makes you want to breathe
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.19,0:36:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 接下来就这么做\N{\rEN}♪ Here's the thing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.15,0:36:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 告诉他你永远不会离开他 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ Tell him that you're never gonna leave him ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.02,0:36:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 告诉他你永远爱他 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ Tell him that you're always gonna love him ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.89,0:36:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 告诉他 告诉他 告诉他 现在就告诉他 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ Tell him, tell him, tell him, tell him right now ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.51,0:36:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我知道一些关于爱的事\N{\rEN}♪ I know something about love
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.77,0:36:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 你必须得表现出来\N{\rEN}♪ You gotta show it and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.16,0:36:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 让他看到头顶的月亮 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ Make him see the moon up above ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.34,0:36:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 去吧 就这么做♪\N{\rEN}♪ Out and get him .Do, do-do
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.60,0:37:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 如果你想让他永远在你身边 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ If you want him to be always by your side ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.17,0:37:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 如果你想让他只想着你 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ If you want him to only think of you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.96,0:37:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 告诉他你永远不会离开他 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ Tell him that you're never gonna leave him ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.40,0:37:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 告诉他你永远爱他 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ Tell him that you're always gonna love him ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.18,0:37:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 告诉他 告诉他 告诉他 现在就告诉他 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ Tell him, tell him, tell him, tell him right now ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.84,0:37:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 自从世界诞生以来\N{\rEN}♪ Ever since the world began
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.58,0:37:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 男人就是这样\N{\rEN}♪ It's been that way for man
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.80,0:37:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 还有女人...\N{\rEN}♪ And women...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.64,0:37:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 唇齿之间\N{\rEN}♪ The touch of your lips
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.82,0:37:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 在我身边\N{\rEN}♪ Next to mine
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.47,0:37:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 让我兴奋\N{\rEN}♪ Gets me excited
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.78,0:37:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我的感觉很棒\N{\rEN}♪ Makes me feel fine
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.61,0:37:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 抚摸你的手\N{\rEN}♪ The touch of your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.09,0:37:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 还有你甜蜜的问候\N{\rEN}♪ Your sweet hello
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.14,0:37:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 你内心燃起的火焰\N{\rEN}♪ The fire inside you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.19,0:38:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 当你紧紧拥抱我时 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ When you're holding me close ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.76,0:38:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 你的爱如此温暖温柔 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ Your love so warm and tender ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.59,0:38:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 你的残酷无比神圣\N{\rEN}♪ Oh. The thrill is so divine
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.77,0:38:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 所有的一切\N{\rEN}♪ It is all these things
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.95,0:38:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 都让我更渴望你\N{\rEN}♪ That make you mine
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.96,0:38:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 如果你要离开\N{\rEN}♪ If you would leave
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.66,0:38:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我肯定会死\N{\rEN}♪ I surely would die
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.36,0:38:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 哪怕是迟了十分钟 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ When you were ten minutes late ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.49,0:38:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我都会难过\N{\rEN}♪ I started to cry
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.76,0:38:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 啊啊啊啊\N{\rEN}♪ Ah, ah, ah
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.41,0:38:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我真的很需要你\N{\rEN}♪ I've got it bad
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.50,0:38:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 但没关系\N{\rEN}♪ But it's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.33,0:38:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 只要你在\N{\rEN}♪ As long as you're here
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.29,0:39:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 每天晚上...\N{\rEN}♪ Every night...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.86,0:39:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我想起荷兰画中的一个女孩\N{\rEN}You remind me of a girl in a Dutch painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.39,0:39:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你有一张不寻常的脸\N{\rEN}You have a strange face.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.18,0:39:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,朴素 但是...\N{\rEN}It's plain, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.22,0:39:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...却很迷人\N{\rEN}...fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.83,0:39:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有一种美丽的...\N{\rEN}It has a beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.36,0:39:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...波澜\N{\rEN}...turbulence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.14,0:39:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢\N{\rEN}I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.97,0:39:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我打赌你一定有过辉煌的梦想\N{\rEN}I bet you have brilliant dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.63,0:39:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,梦想着另一个世界\N{\rEN}I bet you dream of other worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.94,0:39:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你还会梦见我还有我早晨悔恨的样子\N{\rEN}Maybe you'll dream of me and my morning remorse,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.07,0:39:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这是肯定的\N{\rEN}which is certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.29,0:39:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不应该喝酒\N{\rEN}I shouldn't drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.56,0:39:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但我也喝了\N{\rEN}but I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.47,0:39:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.82,0:40:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 桑迪 给我一杯马提尼酒还有火\N{\rEN}Hey, Sandy, can I get a martini and some matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.96,0:40:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,最好小心一点 艾琳\N{\rEN}Better be careful, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.27,0:40:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想跟你爸爸起什么冲突\N{\rEN}I don't want any trouble with your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.23,0:40:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会的\N{\rEN}My dad's not gonna cause any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.36,0:42:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 爸爸\N{\rEN}Dad. Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.49,0:42:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,让我进去\N{\rEN}Dad, can you let me in?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.49,0:42:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\rEN}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.65,0:42:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 老爸\N{\rEN}Hey, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.48,0:42:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,钥匙呢\N{\rEN}Can I have the keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.83,0:42:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,钥匙在哪里\N{\rEN}Can I please have the keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.91,0:42:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你从头到尾读完那本书\N{\rEN}No, you may not have the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.53,0:42:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不然肯定没戏\N{\rEN}Not until you read that book from cover to cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.40,0:42:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我要听清每一个字\N{\rEN}I want to hear every word.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.75,0:43:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你把钥匙放哪儿了\N{\rEN}Where'd you put the keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.11,0:43:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好好找个地方读书吧 艾琳\N{\rEN}Make yourself comfortable, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.80,0:43:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在读完最后一个字之前 你哪儿也去不了\N{\rEN}You're not going anywhere till you read the last word.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.68,0:43:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 这太荒谬了 我还要去上班\N{\rEN}Dad, this is ridiculous. I need to go to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.94,0:43:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你整个晚上都在外面\N{\rEN}Out all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.20,0:43:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还差点把车撞坏了\N{\rEN}Nearly crashed the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.64,0:43:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你自己的呕吐物睡在一起\N{\rEN}Sleeping in your own sick,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.90,0:43:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你想起来要上班了\N{\rEN}and now you're worried about getting to work on time?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.03,0:43:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不能直视你 我觉得很丢人\N{\rEN}I can hardly look at you, I'm so ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.30,0:43:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,雾都孤儿都会知道感激这个家\N{\rEN}Oliver Twist would be grateful for this home,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.69,0:43:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你呢 艾琳\N{\rEN}but you, Eileen,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.56,0:43:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是垃圾 艾琳 垃圾\N{\rEN}you're trash, Eileen, just trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.09,0:43:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我只不过是下班之后跟一个女生出去了\N{\rEN}All I did was go out with a girl from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.57,0:43:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗\N{\rEN}You went out with a girl from work?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.92,0:43:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我有这么好骗吗\N{\rEN}Do I look like I was born yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.35,0:43:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那个男的是谁啊\N{\rEN}Who is he? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.05,0:43:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想知道他是谁\N{\rEN}Who is this boy? I just want to know who he is
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.23,0:43:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,趁着你还没被搞大肚子 把灵魂卖给撒旦之前\N{\rEN}before you get knocked up and sell your soul to Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.18,0:43:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你能把钥匙给我吗\N{\rEN}Can you just give me the keys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.62,0:43:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我要迟到了\N{\rEN}Please! I'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.32,0:43:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你穿成这样哪儿也去不了\N{\rEN}You're not going anywhere dressed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.41,0:43:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我是认真地 艾琳 你怎么敢的\N{\rEN}I mean, really, Eileen, how dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.76,0:43:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你母亲参加我父亲葬礼时穿的衣服\N{\rEN}That's the dress your mother wore to my father's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.59,0:43:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有尊重我们任何一个人\N{\rEN}You got no respect for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.76,0:44:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,马上换掉\N{\rEN}Get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.24,0:44:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,别让任何人看到你穿着这套衣服\N{\rEN}I don't want anyone seeing you in that getup.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.68,0:44:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会以为我已经死了\N{\rEN}They'll think I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.47,0:44:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 邓洛普小姐\N{\rEN}Ah. Miss Dunlop?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.52,0:44:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我能跟你说句话吗\N{\rEN}May I, um, may I have a word?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.69,0:44:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天啊\N{\rEN}Oh, Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.04,0:44:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是关于你父亲的\N{\rEN}It's about your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.57,0:44:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他吗 去吧 他就在里面\N{\rEN}Him? Go talk to him. He's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.74,0:44:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是关于他的枪的\N{\rEN}It's about his gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.09,0:44:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定很精彩\N{\rEN}This oughta be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.35,0:44:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,说吧 巴克\N{\rEN}Pray tell, Buck.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.53,0:44:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 是昨天\N{\rEN}Uh, yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.92,0:44:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们收到了邻居的一些投诉\N{\rEN}we got several complaints from neighbors,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.92,0:44:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还有学校的康尼小姐的投诉\N{\rEN}from Miss Connie down at the school,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.62,0:44:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 邓洛普先生\N{\rEN}that, uh, Chief Dunlop
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.80,0:44:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就坐在朝北的窗户那边\N{\rEN}was sitting in that north-facing window
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.45,0:44:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,然后用枪指着\N{\rEN}and, uh, pointing his weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.02,0:44:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,放学回家的孩子们\N{\rEN}at children walking home from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.29,0:44:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,已经同意把这交给你照管\N{\rEN}He has agreed to relinquish the property into your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.81,0:44:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你保证不对他用的话\N{\rEN}As long as you promise not to use it on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.16,0:44:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他的原话\N{\rEN}His words.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.55,0:44:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗\N{\rEN}May I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.03,0:44:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你想把那把枪当装饰品挂在我身上吗\N{\rEN}Want to hang it on me like an ornament?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.21,0:44:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信邓洛普小姐\N{\rEN}I'm sure that Miss Dunlop
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.08,0:45:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,会好好保养这把武器的 先生\N{\rEN}will take excellent care of the weapon, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.22,0:45:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,巴克 你也看到了 她对待一切事情都是这样\N{\rEN}As she does with all things, Buck, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.67,0:45:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 圣诞节到了\N{\rEN}♪ It's Christmastime
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.45,0:45:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我想见圣诞老人\N{\rEN}♪ And I wanna see Santa Claus
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.72,0:45:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 什么 什么 什么\N{\rEN}♪ What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.98,0:45:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 是的 现在是圣诞节\N{\rEN}♪ Yes, it's Christmastime
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.29,0:45:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我想见圣诞老人\N{\rEN}♪ And I wanna see Santa Claus
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.55,0:45:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 什么 什么 什么\N{\rEN}♪ What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.16,0:45:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 他还有要给我的孩子的礼物呢\N{\rEN}♪ Gonna ask him for my baby
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.51,0:45:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 这不是个好理由吗 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ Ain't that a real good cause? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.13,0:45:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你得告诉我都是谁\N{\rEN}Let me know which ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.30,0:45:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 我会等的\N{\rEN}Sure. I'll hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.87,0:45:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,看看谁来了\N{\rEN}Ah, look what the cat dragged in.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.61,0:45:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,下午好 艾琳\N{\rEN}Good afternoon, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.96,0:45:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来像雏菊一样清新 跟往常一样\N{\rEN}You look fresh as a daisy, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.13,0:45:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我的车出了问题\N{\rEN}I had car trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.40,0:45:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 我肯定会相信你的\N{\rEN}Yeah, I believe the trouble part.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.83,0:45:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,快到圣诞节了 你能让我休息一下吗\N{\rEN}It's almost Christmas. Can you give me a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.18,0:45:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 赶紧工作吧\N{\rEN}No. Get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.14,0:45:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要波尔克的档案\N{\rEN}Okay. I need the Polk file.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.49,0:45:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEN}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.01,0:46:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为她已经拿到手里了\N{\rEN}I think Dr. St. John has it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.06,0:46:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 是的\N{\rEN}Perfect. Yeah, I'm afraid that one
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.54,0:46:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕要等到假期之后了\N{\rEN}will have to wait till after the holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.59,0:46:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要来一位新医生了\N{\rEN}We have a new doctor on staff,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.24,0:46:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那位她不遵守程序\N{\rEN}and, uh, apparently she doesn't follow procedures.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.72,0:46:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她今天没来吗  - 来了又走了\N{\rEN}- She's not in today? - Been and gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.72,0:46:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞节之后还会回来的\N{\rEN}She's gonna be back after Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.98,0:46:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我会的\N{\rEN}Yeah. Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.07,0:46:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 谢谢\N{\rEN}All right, then. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.68,0:46:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,拜\N{\rEN}Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.17,0:46:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是要去哪儿啊\N{\rEN}Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.22,0:46:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,卫生间\N{\rEN}The infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.70,0:46:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得有点儿想吐\N{\rEN}I think something's going around.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.31,0:46:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么在到处乱晃呢\N{\rEN}You look like you've been going around.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.13,0:46:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个酒鬼\N{\rEN}She's a boozer.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.44,0:49:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,爸\N{\rEN}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.97,0:49:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,爸\N{\rEN}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.16,0:49:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,爸\N{\rEN}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.64,0:49:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你能听到我说话吗\N{\rEN}Dad, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.90,0:49:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 你能听到我说话吗\N{\rEN}Dad, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.47,0:49:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在那儿做什么 - 我需要我的枪\N{\rEN}- What were you doing up there? - I need my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.25,0:49:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 坐起来 - 有人在追我\N{\rEN}- Sit up. - It's after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.34,0:49:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没人在追你\N{\rEN}Nobody's after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.34,0:50:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,坐起来 坐起来\N{\rEN}Sit up. Sit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.18,0:50:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,乔安妮\N{\rEN}Joanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.79,0:50:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是你吗乔安妮\N{\rEN}That you, Joanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.83,0:50:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rEN}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.84,0:50:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,乔安妮 乔安妮\N{\rEN}Joanie. Joanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.45,0:50:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,乔安妮\N{\rEN}Joanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.06,0:50:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\rEN}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.76,0:50:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不用大惊小怪的 乔安妮\N{\rEN}Quit your fussing, Joanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.99,0:50:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经给他缝了伤口\N{\rEN}We stitched him up,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.38,0:50:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,排除了脑震荡的可能\N{\rEN}and I don't think he has a concussion,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.99,0:50:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但他的血液酒精浓度\N{\rEN}but his blood alcohol level
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.47,0:50:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有0.17\N{\rEN}is point one-seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.12,0:50:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,肝硬化的指标很危险 而且还浑身都是淤青\N{\rEN}His liver's enlarged, and he's covered in bruises.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.21,0:50:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是要怪你 亲爱的 但是 呃…\N{\rEN}I'm not blaming you, honey, but, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.65,0:50:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好 当然\N{\rEN}Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.04,0:50:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是到底是谁让他这样啊\N{\rEN}Hey, who's letting him live like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.78,0:50:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 我妈妈去世了 他现在也没有工作\N{\rEN}I don't know. My mom died, and he doesn't have a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.09,0:50:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他还能做什么\N{\rEN}What else is he supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.74,0:50:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可是总不能整天喝酒吧\N{\rEN}Yeah, there are men who don't drink all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.40,0:50:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rEN}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.23,0:51:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我知道这对你来说很难 但是 呃…\N{\rEN}Look, I know this is hard for you, but, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.97,0:51:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他不喝酒的话 他只是有可能活不下去了\N{\rEN}if he stops drinking, he might die,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.27,0:51:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果他继续喝酒 那他肯定就没命了\N{\rEN}but if he keeps drinking, it'll definitely kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.02,0:51:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,除此之外我也不知道还能跟你说什么了\N{\rEN}I don't know what else to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.94,0:51:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下 爸爸\N{\rEN}Sit down, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.34,0:51:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,医生告诉我你会死的\N{\rEN}The doctor told me you're gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.43,0:51:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 他是不会死吗\N{\rEN}Oh, like he's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.43,0:51:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他说 如果你如果再这样喝酒\N{\rEN}He said, if you keep drinking like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.22,0:51:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那些酒精真的会害死你的\N{\rEN}it'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.48,0:51:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,去他的吧\N{\rEN}Screw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.13,0:51:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就是在那家医院杀了你的母亲\N{\rEN}You know they killed your mother at that hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.57,0:51:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们欠我的可不仅仅是缝个针这么简单\N{\rEN}They owe me more than stitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.92,0:51:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你能往后靠吗\N{\rEN}Can you lean back?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.92,0:51:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\rEN}Course I can lean back.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.27,0:51:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,难不成我连怎么睡觉都不会了吗\N{\rEN}You don't think I know how to go to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.54,0:51:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,得了 我还是要喝一杯\N{\rEN}Well, I need a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.54,0:51:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\rEN}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.84,0:51:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我不要睡在这里\N{\rEN}And anyway, I do not sleep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.50,0:51:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这里会闹鬼 - 求你了 爸爸\N{\rEN}- It's haunted. - Please, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.32,0:51:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我给你一瓶酒的话 你能躺下吗\N{\rEN}If I get you a bottle, will you lie down?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.55,0:51:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我想和我女儿喝一杯\N{\rEN}No. I want to have a drink with my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.68,0:52:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你这几天不太一样了\N{\rEN}You're different these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.64,0:52:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就快变得很有趣了\N{\rEN}You're almost interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.04,0:52:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你用工作赚的钱都去做什么了\N{\rEN}What are you doing with all the money you make at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.04,0:52:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么不给自己买件衣服呢\N{\rEN}Why don't you ever buy your own clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.18,0:52:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我还记得那件外套\N{\rEN}I remember that coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.40,0:52:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得你妈妈...\N{\rEN}I remember your mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.19,0:52:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我穿起来怎么样\N{\rEN}How does it look on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.06,0:52:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 反正你妈妈穿那件外套看起来很漂亮\N{\rEN}Well, your mother looked beautiful in that coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.11,0:52:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是她从精神病院出来的时候\N{\rEN}I bought it for her to wear
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.02,0:52:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我买给她穿的\N{\rEN}when she got out of the bughouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.77,0:52:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直爱着你的母亲\N{\rEN}I always loved your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.25,0:52:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你是怎么看的\N{\rEN}No matter what you thought it looked like,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.77,0:52:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都爱着她\N{\rEN}I always loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.04,0:52:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他们都是怎么说我的\N{\rEN}And I know what people say about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.30,0:52:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说是我逼疯她的 因为我很难搞\N{\rEN}They say I made her crazy 'cause I'm a hard-ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.18,0:53:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能确实朝她喊过几次\N{\rEN}And I may have yelled a few times,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.00,0:53:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但是她总会原谅我\N{\rEN}but she always forgave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.05,0:53:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们彼此相爱\N{\rEN}Because we loved each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.62,0:53:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,爱会让你疯狂 艾琳\N{\rEN}Love will make you crazy, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.02,0:53:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能永远都不会明白这一点\N{\rEN}You'll probably never understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.50,0:53:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\rEN}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.67,0:53:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人...\N{\rEN}Some people...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.81,0:53:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们才是真正的人\N{\rEN}they're the real people.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.20,0:53:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是那些电影里你正在看着的人\N{\rEN}Like in a movie, they're the ones you're watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.34,0:53:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他们才是主角\N{\rEN}They're the ones making moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.08,0:53:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,而其他人...\N{\rEN}And the other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.21,0:53:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...他们只是用来当配角 填补空白用的\N{\rEN}...they're just there filling the space,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.96,0:53:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你会觉得这是理所当然的\N{\rEN}and you take 'em for granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.31,0:53:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还会觉得这不是很容易吗\N{\rEN}You think, "They're easy."
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.26,0:53:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就是这样 拿一分 留一分\N{\rEN}Take a penny, leave a penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.71,0:53:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是你 艾琳\N{\rEN}That's you, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.58,0:54:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你就跟他们一样\N{\rEN}You're one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.22,0:54:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么 不用锁\N{\rEN}What are you doing? You don't gotta lock it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.30,0:54:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\rEN}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.05,0:54:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 快点\N{\rEN}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.39,0:54:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 太冷了\N{\rEN}Come on. It's cold out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.18,0:54:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,快点儿\N{\rEN}Come on. Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.18,0:54:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,把门打开\N{\rEN}Open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.79,0:54:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真他妈重\N{\rEN}Fucking heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.06,0:54:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,把酒拿来\N{\rEN}Give me my fucking drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.61,0:55:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳\N{\rEN}Eileen!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.66,0:55:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳\N{\rEN}Eileen!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.01,0:55:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什么了 爸爸\N{\rEN}What, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.49,0:55:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,电话响了\N{\rEN}Phone rang.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.10,0:55:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有个女人找你\N{\rEN}Some woman looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.67,0:55:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你说了什么吗\N{\rEN}What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.89,0:55:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\rEN}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.02,0:55:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都没说\N{\rEN}I know nothing. I said nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.21,0:55:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rEN}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.34,0:55:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 圣诞天使\N{\rEN}Hello, Christmas angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.30,0:55:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞贝卡\N{\rEN}Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.13,0:55:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我只是想到你\N{\rEN}Look, I was just thinking of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.56,0:55:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我也不知道\N{\rEN}and, well, I-I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.00,0:55:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,平安夜你有什么计划\N{\rEN}what you're planning for Christmas Eve,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.44,0:55:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你愿意过来\N{\rEN}but I thought maybe you'd like to come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.44,0:55:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以放一些唱片\N{\rEN}There are some records we could play,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.87,0:56:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果一切顺利的话 也可以跳舞\N{\rEN}and maybe dance again if all goes well.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.01,0:56:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 除非你有更好的提议\N{\rEN}Unless you have a better offer, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.71,0:56:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有比这更好的了\N{\rEN}I don't have a better offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.06,0:56:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所以你会来吗 - 是的\N{\rEN}- So you'll come? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.80,0:56:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我把地址给你\N{\rEN}Let me give you the address.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.71,0:56:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等\N{\rEN}Okay. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.11,0:56:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,枫树街32号\N{\rEN}It's 32 Maple Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.55,0:56:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚见\N{\rEN}So see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.50,0:56:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再见 - 再见\N{\rEN}- Bye. - Bye.
