Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.00,0:56:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 在我身边\N{\rEN}♪ Next to mine
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.83,0:56:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 让我兴奋\N{\rEN}♪ Gets me excited
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.88,0:56:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 让我感觉很好 哦 哦\N{\rEN}♪ Makes me feel fine. Oh, oh
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.53,0:56:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 抚摸着你的手\N{\rEN}♪ The touch of your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.10,0:56:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 你甜蜜的问候\N{\rEN}♪ Your sweet hello
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.02,0:56:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 你内心的火焰 .\N{\rEN}♪ The fire inside you
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.24,0:57:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 当你紧紧拥抱我时 ♪\N{\rEN}♪ When you're holding me close ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.07,0:57:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 你的爱如此温暖\N{\rEN}♪ Your love so warm
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.33,0:57:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 又温柔...\N{\rEN}♪ And tender...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.11,0:57:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你来啦\N{\rEN}Y-You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.33,0:57:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真是圣诞节的奇迹\N{\rEN}It's a Christmas miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.64,0:57:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我花了这么长时间\N{\rEN}Sorry it took me so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.47,0:57:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得那只猫着魔了\N{\rEN}I think that cat's possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.34,0:57:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐\N{\rEN}Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.43,0:58:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,太贴心了\N{\rEN}Oh. Aren't you a peach?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.91,0:58:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,请进 快请进\N{\rEN}Come in! Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.83,0:58:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳 嗯\N{\rEN}Eileen, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.22,0:58:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 这个地方太乱了\N{\rEN}I'm sorry the place is such a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.92,0:58:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我实在...我是说 我有试着整理一下\N{\rEN}I-I haven't... I mean, I tried to clean it up a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.35,0:58:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但这真的超出了我的能力范围\N{\rEN}but it's just beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.75,0:58:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你不会觉得不舒服\N{\rEN}I hope it doesn't make you uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.01,0:58:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把酒打开吧\N{\rEN}Let's open this wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.01,0:58:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,快坐 快坐\N{\rEN}Uh, sit down. Sit down. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.45,0:58:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你没有开的太久 会很远吗\N{\rEN}I hope you didn't have to drive far. Was it far?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.89,0:58:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不会 就是随便开开\N{\rEN}Uh, no. I drive all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.89,0:58:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,把外套给我吧\N{\rEN}Let me take your coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.20,0:58:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢 - 天啊\N{\rEN}- Thanks. - Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.33,0:58:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,摸起来真舒服\N{\rEN}It's so nice and soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.77,0:58:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我母亲的\N{\rEN}It's my mother's.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.42,0:58:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 她一定是一位真正优雅的女士\N{\rEN}Well, uh, she must have been a real classy lady
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.47,0:58:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,才能有你这么优秀的女儿\N{\rEN}to have such a classy daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.73,0:58:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,她确实如此\N{\rEN}She was something of a clotheshorse, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.47,0:58:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,希望是你喜欢的那种\N{\rEN}I hope it's a kind you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.17,0:58:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定很好吃\N{\rEN}Oh. I'm sure it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.78,0:58:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,喝酒也不错\N{\rEN}Drink sounds nice, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.65,0:58:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我来找找开瓶器在哪里\N{\rEN}Let's see where the corkscrew's hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.44,0:58:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 你知道吧\N{\rEN}Uh, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.35,0:58:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我最近实在是太忙了\N{\rEN}I have just been so busy lately
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.22,0:58:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,放哪里去了呢...\N{\rEN}that I can't seem to remember where the...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.62,0:59:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定就在这摊东西里面\N{\rEN}But it's got to be here under all this mess, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.45,0:59:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\rEN}You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.27,0:59:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有个很手巧的年轻的哲学博士以前教过我一招儿\N{\rEN}A very handy young PhD student once taught me a trick
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.23,0:59:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,在你被困的情况下要怎么打开一个瓶子\N{\rEN}for how to open a bottle if you're ever stranded
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.59,0:59:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有开瓶器\N{\rEN}without a corkscrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.85,0:59:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哲学家们才是最大的酒鬼\N{\rEN}Philosophers are always the biggest drunks.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.60,0:59:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然他本来就有点儿可爱\N{\rEN}Although he was kind of cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.86,0:59:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,尤金·亨德森 哈佛大学\N{\rEN}Eugene Henderson, Harvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.52,0:59:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你还能这样呢\N{\rEN}I had no idea you could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.61,0:59:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒的一招儿\N{\rEN}That was a great trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.87,0:59:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,现在需要的就是酒杯了\N{\rEN}Now we need some glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.10,0:59:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,敬艾琳 我的圣诞救星\N{\rEN}So to Eileen, my Christmas savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.62,0:59:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,救星吗\N{\rEN}Savior?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.10,0:59:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么也没做\N{\rEN}I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.40,0:59:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,成为我的朋友\N{\rEN}Well, you're being a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.97,0:59:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这还不够吗 干杯\N{\rEN}That's everything. Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.33,0:59:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 太可怕了\N{\rEN}God, that's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.76,0:59:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那...\N{\rEN}No. That's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.24,1:00:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,味道好浓\N{\rEN}...punch of flavor.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.20,1:00:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是席拉（一种葡萄酒）\N{\rEN}That's what a Syrah is.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.73,1:00:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你没有花太多钱\N{\rEN}Hope you haven't spent too much on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.64,1:00:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,敬...\N{\rEN}To...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.00,1:00:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,敬耶稣基督\N{\rEN}To Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.95,1:00:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,生日快乐\N{\rEN}Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.66,1:00:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你一个人住在这里吗\N{\rEN}Do you live here alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.92,1:00:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEN}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.05,1:00:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是的\N{\rEN}Oh, uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.49,1:00:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我 呃...不 我不能忍受有室友\N{\rEN}I, uh... No, I can't have roommates.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.58,1:00:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我 嗯 我喜欢独处\N{\rEN}I, um, I like my own space.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.71,1:00:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我也能很高兴\N{\rEN}I still like to have fun,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.10,1:00:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 呃 我还能弄出很大的声音\N{\rEN}and, uh, I can make a lot of noise.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.37,1:00:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,还有把一切都弄乱 你也看到了\N{\rEN}And, uh, I can make a mess, as you can see,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.80,1:00:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 还可以随心所欲地放歌儿\N{\rEN}but, uh, I can play music as loud as I want to.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.46,1:00:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,还能...\N{\rEN}I can...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.76,1:00:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,随心所欲地尖叫\N{\rEN}I can scream as loud as I want to.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.47,1:00:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\rEN}I can't stand roommates, either.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.82,1:00:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,上大学的时候 我都必须锁门…\N{\rEN}In college, I had to lock my door...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.73,1:00:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 你上大学的时候\N{\rEN}Oh, that's right. You were in college.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.69,1:00:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你学的什么\N{\rEN}What'd you study?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.69,1:00:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就是些必修课\N{\rEN}Just the required courses.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.39,1:00:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 如果我没有辍学的话\N{\rEN}Um, if I hadn't left,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.13,1:01:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我最后可能也会做秘书\N{\rEN}I probably would have ended up a secretary anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.70,1:01:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳 这不是你真正的样子\N{\rEN}Eileen, you're not really a secretary.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.39,1:01:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,默里夫人和史蒂文斯夫人 她们才是这样\N{\rEN}Mrs. Murray and Mrs. Stevens, they're secretaries,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.09,1:01:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她们总是别人说什么就做什么\N{\rEN}'cause they do what they're told,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.62,1:01:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是她们过得这么悲惨还有令人讨厌的原因\N{\rEN}and that's why they're miserable and nasty.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.36,1:01:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但我相信 你的人生还有美好的未来\N{\rEN}But you, you got a big life ahead of you, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.19,1:01:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 希望我的人生不会就到此为止了\N{\rEN}Okay. I'm not a real secretary.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.58,1:01:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不会\N{\rEN}No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.41,1:01:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你很聪明\N{\rEN}'Cause you're smart.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.80,1:01:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你也很好奇 不是吗\N{\rEN}And you're curious, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.55,1:01:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我在学校的表现从来都不是很好\N{\rEN}Mm, I never really did very good in school,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.16,1:01:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我觉得自己只是一个普通人\N{\rEN}so I'm just kind of average, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.07,1:01:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 别这么说 艾琳\N{\rEN}Oh, don't say that, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.81,1:01:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,永远不要这么说 你...\N{\rEN}Never say that. Do you...?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.30,1:01:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你真以为自己很普通吗\N{\rEN}You really think you're a normal person?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.65,1:01:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,普通怎么了\N{\rEN}Normal how?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.00,1:01:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我确实是一个糟糕的女主人\N{\rEN}I really am a bad hostess.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.79,1:01:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们 呃...\N{\rEN}Maybe we'll, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.18,1:01:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,吃点儿东西吧 这样才像样\N{\rEN}We'll feel better if we eat something.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.66,1:01:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我挺好的\N{\rEN}I feel fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.71,1:02:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我能用下你的洗手间吗\N{\rEN}Can I use your bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.98,1:02:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\rEN}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.28,1:02:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就在楼上\N{\rEN}Just up the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.87,1:02:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是另一个门 右边的\N{\rEN}It's the other door, on the right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.36,1:04:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\rEN}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.76,1:04:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么好抱歉的\N{\rEN}What do you have to be sorry for?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.93,1:04:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,来嘛 吃吧\N{\rEN}Go on. Go on. Eat. Eat. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.93,1:04:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,还有那个腌黄瓜\N{\rEN}Have a pickle, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.41,1:04:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我们还需要什么小奶酪刀\N{\rEN}Why do we need a little, uh, cheese knife?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.33,1:04:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就为了不弄脏手\N{\rEN}To keep our hands clean?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.85,1:04:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这一切都很荒谬\N{\rEN}No. It's all ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.64,1:04:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都是\N{\rEN}Everything is.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.38,1:04:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所有这些愚蠢的传统\N{\rEN}All these stupid traditions,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.73,1:04:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就跟圣诞节那个时候的监狱还有那个典狱长\N{\rEN}like the-the warden and his prison at Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.30,1:04:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什​​么意思\N{\rEN}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.82,1:04:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我试图解释事情需要怎么改变\N{\rEN}I've tried explaining how things need to change,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.35,1:04:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但他只关心\N{\rEN}but all he cares about
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.70,1:04:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那些男孩儿晚上在牢房里自慰的时候\N{\rEN}is whether or not the boys are gonna think about me
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.48,1:04:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,性幻想的对象是不是我\N{\rEN}while they molest themselves in their cells at night.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.74,1:04:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿不会\N{\rEN}God forbid.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.53,1:04:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,摩尔黑德有严格的\N{\rEN}There's a strict
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.88,1:04:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,禁止手淫的规定\N{\rEN}no masturbation policy at Moorehead.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.84,1:04:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这在监狱是违法的\N{\rEN}It's illegal to get off in prison.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.58,1:04:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 对吧\N{\rEN}You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.84,1:04:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好像那些有性高潮的人\N{\rEN}As if that's the downfall of civilization,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.84,1:04:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一种文明的衰败一样\N{\rEN}people having orgasms.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.93,1:04:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能指望男人来解决任何问题\N{\rEN}You can't count on men to fix anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.98,1:05:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,人们羞于面对自己的欲望\N{\rEN}People are so ashamed of their desires,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.37,1:05:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是男人\N{\rEN}especially men.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.56,1:05:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳……\N{\rEN}Eileen...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.08,1:05:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...你现在可能已经知道了\N{\rEN}...as you can probably tell by now,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.08,1:05:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我的生活方式与大多数人都不太一样\N{\rEN}I live a little differently than most people.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.87,1:05:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你的房子...很好\N{\rEN}No, your house i-is nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.87,1:05:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不是说这个  - 很舒服\N{\rEN}- No. - It's cozy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.05,1:05:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的不是房子 我是说...\N{\rEN}I don't mean the house. I mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.48,1:05:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我有自己的想法\N{\rEN}I have my own ideas.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.97,1:05:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们有些想法是一样的\N{\rEN}Maybe you and I share some of those ideas.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.49,1:05:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有哪些呢\N{\rEN}What kind of ideas do we share?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.46,1:05:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以跟你说吗\N{\rEN}May I confide in you?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.33,1:05:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\rEN}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.51,1:05:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是关于李·波尔克的\N{\rEN}It's about Lee Polk.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.86,1:05:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是吗  - 是的\N{\rEN}- It is? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.90,1:05:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你说说 亲爱的...\N{\rEN}Tell me, honey...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.99,1:06:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,…什么会让一个人想要杀死自己的父亲呢\N{\rEN}...what would make a person want to kill their father?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.04,1:06:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都想杀死自己的父亲\N{\rEN}Everybody wants to kill their father.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.22,1:06:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是这样的 谁告诉你的\N{\rEN}No, they don't. Who told you that?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.79,1:06:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 想想吧 艾琳\N{\rEN}Really, think about it, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.53,1:06:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,因为李可是偷偷溜进了他父母的卧室\N{\rEN}Because Lee snuck into his parents' bedroom
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.79,1:06:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,还是在半夜...\N{\rEN}in the middle of the night...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.10,1:06:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...砍断了他父亲的喉咙\N{\rEN}...hacked through his father's throat
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.84,1:06:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就用一把旧菜刀\N{\rEN}with an old kitchen knife,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.41,1:06:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而且在他的胸部那里砍了好几刀\N{\rEN}and stabbed him in the chest repeatedly.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.24,1:06:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他的母亲声说她还以为有人入室盗窃\N{\rEN}His mother claimed she thought there'd been a break-in.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.20,1:06:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,遇到这种事你怎么睡得着\N{\rEN}How do you sleep through something like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.85,1:06:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rEN}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.37,1:06:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不知道 所以我才叫她来\N{\rEN}You don't. That's why I called her in.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.64,1:06:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你当时也在那里\N{\rEN}I mean, you were there.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.16,1:06:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那个可怜的男孩几乎不敢看她 所以…\N{\rEN}The poor boy could barely look at her, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.73,1:06:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以后来我就直截了当地问他\N{\rEN}so afterwards, I just asked him point-blank.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.38,1:06:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我说...\N{\rEN}I said...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.39,1:06:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我问他他爸爸都对他做了什么\N{\rEN}I said, "What'd your father do to you?"
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.13,1:06:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"你为什么要这样对待你父亲的尸体"\N{\rEN}"What made you want to do that to your father's body?"
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.22,1:06:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他没花了几分钟就全都说了\N{\rEN}And he spilled it all in a matter of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.44,1:06:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,以前从来没有人费心去问过他\N{\rEN}Nobody had ever bothered to ask him before.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.27,1:06:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人想过还要问他\N{\rEN}No one had thought to ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.58,1:07:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想知道吗\N{\rEN}Wouldn't you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.58,1:07:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你不好奇吗\N{\rEN}Wouldn't you be curious?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.62,1:07:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇\N{\rEN}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.11,1:07:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道吗\N{\rEN}Do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.03,1:07:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEN}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.03,1:07:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳 你永远不能告诉任何人 你明白吗\N{\rEN}Eileen, you can never tell anyone. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.68,1:07:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白...答应我\N{\rEN}You understa... Promise me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.95,1:07:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\rEN}Promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.00,1:07:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你首先需要知道的是\N{\rEN}The first thing you need to know,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.56,1:07:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我的家\N{\rEN}this isn't my house.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.00,1:07:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是波尔克的家\N{\rEN}This is the Polk house.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.26,1:07:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,波克夫人被我绑在楼下\N{\rEN}I have Mrs. Polk tied up downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.97,1:07:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳 艾琳\N{\rEN}Eileen. Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.84,1:07:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳\N{\rEN}Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.37,1:07:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳 别走\N{\rEN}Eileen, please wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.76,1:07:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳 拜托了\N{\rEN}Eileen, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.02,1:07:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我自己就可以的 艾琳\N{\rEN}I thought I could do this alone, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.81,1:07:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要走 艾琳\N{\rEN}Please don't go. Eileen!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.98,1:08:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,别走 拜托了\N{\rEN}Please, don't go. Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.03,1:08:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你邀请我过来是因为你喜欢我\N{\rEN}I thought you invited me over here 'cause you liked me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.90,1:08:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 当然是这样\N{\rEN}Oh, I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.77,1:08:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是这样 抱歉 抱歉 艾琳\N{\rEN}I do. I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry. Please, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.52,1:08:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 拜托 艾琳 请给我一点时间\N{\rEN}Just pl-please, Eileen. Just give me a moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.13,1:08:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,让我解释一下\N{\rEN}Please just let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.61,1:08:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要...\N{\rEN}I need...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.17,1:08:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要一个朋友\N{\rEN}I need a friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.88,1:08:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天下午来过这里\N{\rEN}I came here yesterday afternoon
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.44,1:08:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,跟波尔克夫人谈了话\N{\rEN}to talk to Mrs. Polk.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.05,1:08:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我说我看得出来她跟李会面后\N{\rEN}I said I could see that she was upset
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.58,1:08:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一直很沮丧\N{\rEN}after our meeting with Lee,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.06,1:08:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我问她有什么想跟我说的吗\N{\rEN}was there anything she wanted to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.06,1:08:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,她说没什么 所以我...\N{\rEN}She said, "Nothing," so I...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.32,1:08:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我追问她\N{\rEN}I pressed her.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.02,1:08:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我把李告诉我的话告诉了她\N{\rEN}I told her what Lee had told me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.24,1:08:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她向我吐口水 说我变态了\N{\rEN}She spat at me, called me the pervert,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.16,1:08:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,然后称她的丈夫为圣人\N{\rEN}then called her husband a saint,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.86,1:08:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我留下了我的名片 让她考虑一下\N{\rEN}and I left my card, told her to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.64,1:08:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道她不会打电话来 然后我就离开了\N{\rEN}I knew she wouldn't call. Then I left.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.13,1:08:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 我整晚都无法入睡\N{\rEN}Now, I couldn't sleep last night.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.43,1:08:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我...\N{\rEN}'Cause I...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.05,1:09:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一直在想李跟我说的话\N{\rEN}I couldn't stop thinking about what Lee had told me,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.70,1:09:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他父亲做的那些事\N{\rEN}what his father had done,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.22,1:09:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,以及他的母亲是如何纵容这一切的\N{\rEN}and how his mother had let it happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.10,1:09:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不记得自己是怎么开车过来的 我很生气\N{\rEN}I don't even remember the drive over here, I was so angry.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.92,1:09:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我就把她挤到一边\N{\rEN}Suddenly I was pushing past her,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.67,1:09:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,质问她怎么能这么做\N{\rEN}saying, "How could you do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.19,1:09:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能纵容这一切呢\N{\rEN}How could you be complicit in such torture?"
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.10,1:09:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她恶狠狠地回绝我\N{\rEN}And she snapped.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.98,1:09:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她还打了我 你看\N{\rEN}She attacked me. See?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.37,1:09:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吗\N{\rEN}See?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.07,1:09:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我只能还手保护自己\N{\rEN}So I defended myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.68,1:09:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们吵架了 我...我不知道发生了什么\N{\rEN}We fought, and I... I don't know what happened,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.85,1:09:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但不知怎么的 我们从楼梯上摔到了地下室\N{\rEN}but somehow we fell down the stairs to the basement.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.25,1:09:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为她会杀了我\N{\rEN}I-I thought she was gonna kill me,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.81,1:09:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我用椅子打了她 然后把她绑了起来\N{\rEN}so I hit her with a chair and tied her up.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.47,1:09:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我试图理性地跟她说话\N{\rEN}I tried to talk to her rationally,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.60,1:09:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,跟她解释我是来帮助李的\N{\rEN}to explain that I was here to help Lee,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.26,1:09:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她允许的话 我也可以帮助她\N{\rEN}that-that I could help her, too, if she'd let me,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.74,1:09:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但…但她只是不停地尖叫\N{\rEN}but... but she just kept screaming
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.09,1:09:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,说...我绑架了她 她的丈夫是一名警察\N{\rEN}that-that I'd kidnapped her and her husband was a cop
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.35,1:09:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她说我这是要蹲监狱的\N{\rEN}and I was gonna go to jail.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.14,1:09:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我在卫生间里发现了一些可待因（用鸦片制成的止痛镇咳药）\N{\rEN}So I found some codeine in a bathroom,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.01,1:09:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我给她吃了为了让她安静下来\N{\rEN}and got her to be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.67,1:09:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我就给你打了电话\N{\rEN}Then I called you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.80,1:10:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道 这里我谁都不认识\N{\rEN}Because, as you can see, I'm in a bit of a pinch.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.59,1:10:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我能怎么办\N{\rEN}What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.81,1:10:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要波尔克夫人承认\N{\rEN}I need Mrs. Polk to confess,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.16,1:10:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要一名证人 二对一\N{\rEN}and I need a witness, two against one.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.29,1:10:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白吗\N{\rEN}You understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.73,1:10:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我不能进监狱\N{\rEN}Oh, I can't go to jail.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.48,1:10:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEN}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.23,1:10:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEN}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.37,1:10:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,在这儿等着\N{\rEN}Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.59,1:10:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳 等等...\N{\rEN}Eileen. Wait...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.14,1:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不敢相信\N{\rEN}It's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.36,1:11:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么有枪\N{\rEN}Why do you have that?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.84,1:11:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么把它带到这里来\N{\rEN}Why did you bring that around here?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.10,1:11:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸病了\N{\rEN}My dad's sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.41,1:11:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,拿起它 我看看你是怎么握枪的\N{\rEN}Pick it up, and show me how you're gonna hold it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.15,1:11:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好 艾琳\N{\rEN}That's very good, Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.29,1:11:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rEN}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.17,1:11:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静点儿\N{\rEN}Be cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.25,1:12:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我们真相吧 波尔克夫人\N{\rEN}Just tell us the truth, Mrs. Polk,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.21,1:12:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会放了你的\N{\rEN}and we'll let you go free.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.30,1:12:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,家人可以治愈一切\N{\rEN}Families can heal.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.52,1:12:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你并不是一个失败的人 没有人是\N{\rEN}You're not a lost cause. No one is.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.70,1:12:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嫁给这样的男人\N{\rEN}It can't have been easy,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.05,1:12:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对你来说肯定不容易\N{\rEN}being married to a man like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.66,1:12:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定过得很艰难\N{\rEN}You're obviously having a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.36,1:12:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不跟我们说说这间房子里都发生过什么\N{\rEN}Why don't you tell us what happened in this house,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.36,1:12:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你要纵容而且还帮助你的丈夫做那样的事\N{\rEN}why you helped your husband do what he did?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.63,1:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就行了\N{\rEN}And then we'll be even,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.50,1:13:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人会受伤 然后…\N{\rEN}and we can all walk out of here, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.68,1:13:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以想办法帮助李\N{\rEN}and we can figure out how to help Lee.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.17,1:13:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的给我解开 放开我\N{\rEN}Fucking untie me! Untie me!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.56,1:13:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我\N{\rEN}Let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.04,1:13:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个疯女人 滚出我家\N{\rEN}You crazy bitch, get out of my house!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.00,1:13:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你有大麻烦了 你以为你会...\N{\rEN}You're in big trouble, you think you're gonna
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.48,1:13:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 逃过去吗 - 艾琳\N{\rEN}- get away with this! - Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.74,1:13:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你会蹲很久的监狱\N{\rEN}You're going to jail for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.79,1:13:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她到底在这里做什么\N{\rEN}What the hell is she doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.10,1:13:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里做什么\N{\rEN}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.66,1:13:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的觉得你应该告诉我们真相\N{\rEN}I really think you need to tell us the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.71,1:13:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈在说什么\N{\rEN}What the hell are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.49,1:13:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不说...\N{\rEN}If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.93,1:13:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以把你绑在这儿\N{\rEN}we could leave you down here tied up,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.80,1:13:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人能找到你\N{\rEN}no one to find you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.02,1:13:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人如果没有食物和水\N{\rEN}The human body can't live very long
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.54,1:13:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是活不了太久的\N{\rEN}without food and water.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.24,1:13:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你肯定还要上厕所\N{\rEN}Sooner or later, you're gonna need to take a shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.50,1:13:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你只能拉在自己身上了\N{\rEN}I guess you're just gonna have to shit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.85,1:13:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还有尿\N{\rEN}And piss.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.77,1:13:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定不会很好受\N{\rEN}It's not gonna feel very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.34,1:13:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不怕你\N{\rEN}I'm not scared of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.43,1:13:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识你\N{\rEN}I know you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.64,1:13:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你爸爸是谁\N{\rEN}I know who your dad is.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.25,1:13:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你认识我爸爸 那么你应该感到害怕\N{\rEN}If you know my dad, then you oughta be scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.47,1:14:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 害怕一个玩弄女人的醉鬼吗\N{\rEN}Yeah? Scared of a womanizing, drunk piece of shit
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.74,1:14:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都知道到底谁才是疯子\N{\rEN}who everybody knows is batshit crazy?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.91,1:14:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为他自己没有问题吗\N{\rEN}You think he didn't have problems of his own?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.44,1:14:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为他没有自己的小秘密 是吗\N{\rEN}You think he didn't have secrets of his own, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.31,1:14:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得你妈妈不知道吗\N{\rEN}You think your mom didn't know about 'em?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.05,1:14:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为...\N{\rEN}Think it didn't...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.96,1:14:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我他妈要杀了你\N{\rEN}I am going to fucking kill you
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.75,1:14:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你还不说的话\N{\rEN}if you don't start talking right now!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.06,1:14:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\rEN}Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.89,1:14:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,别杀我\N{\rEN}Please, don't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.06,1:14:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你都招了 我就不会杀你\N{\rEN}I won't have to kill you if you talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.73,1:14:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\rEN}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.30,1:14:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 拜托了\N{\rEN}No, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.26,1:14:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她也帮不了你 说吧\N{\rEN}She's not gonna help you. Talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.44,1:14:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你坦白 否则我帮不了你\N{\rEN}I can't help you unless you confess.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.37,1:15:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEN}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.25,1:15:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你赢了\N{\rEN}You win.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.60,1:15:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,当你结婚了\N{\rEN}When you get married
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.13,1:15:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还有了孩子...\N{\rEN}and you have children...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.79,1:15:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,结婚的时候你要宣誓\N{\rEN}You take an oath when you get married
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.58,1:15:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,尊重并服从你的丈夫\N{\rEN}to honor and obey your husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.01,1:15:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会明白这一点\N{\rEN}You wouldn't understand that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.80,1:15:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,起初 我...\N{\rEN}At first, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.80,1:15:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,起初 我只是 我以为米奇\N{\rEN}At first, I just, I thought Mitch
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.89,1:15:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,只是在睡梦中检查李\N{\rEN}was just checking on him in his sleep,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.72,1:15:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所有父亲都会这样\N{\rEN}you know, like any father would,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.46,1:15:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,和他一样 他只是想确定一下\N{\rEN}like he, he just wanted to be sure
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.77,1:16:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他的儿子安然无恙地躺在床上\N{\rEN}his son was safe and sound in bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.03,1:16:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有时我会...\N{\rEN}Sometimes I'd...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.78,1:16:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...感觉他起床了\N{\rEN}...feel him getting out of bed,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.52,1:16:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候我能感觉到他回来了\N{\rEN}and sometimes I'd just feel him when he'd come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.61,1:16:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,而他也会...\N{\rEN}And he'd...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.31,1:16:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,吻我或者...\N{\rEN}kiss me or...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.92,1:16:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,抱住我 然后……\N{\rEN}hold me and...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.92,1:16:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\rEN}You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.32,1:16:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,自从李出生后\N{\rEN}And we hadn't really been together
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.67,1:16:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就没有过性生活了\N{\rEN}since Lee'd been born.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.58,1:16:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但后来我...\N{\rEN}But then I...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.89,1:16:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现自己下面有些感染\N{\rEN}I started getting these infections down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.12,1:16:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为这是我的问题\N{\rEN}I figured it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.77,1:16:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,后来我就想知道是不是米奇\N{\rEN}And then I wondered if Mitch
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.34,1:16:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,把脏东西带回家的\N{\rEN}had brought something home with him, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.83,1:16:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,然后有一次...\N{\rEN}Then one time...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.57,1:17:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我半夜起来了\N{\rEN}I got up in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.18,1:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我也忘了是为什么\N{\rEN}I don't remember why.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.44,1:17:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是要喝水吧 我也不记得了\N{\rEN}Glass of water? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.63,1:17:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,也许这就是一场梦吧\N{\rEN}I thought-I thought maybe it was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.72,1:17:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我...\N{\rEN}I...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.94,1:17:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我走进去看了看\N{\rEN}I went-I went and looked in.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.82,1:17:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时没有马上反应过来\N{\rEN}It didn't dawn on me right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.60,1:17:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓 我...\N{\rEN}You know, I-I swear to you. I...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.34,1:17:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说...\N{\rEN}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.91,1:17:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不会期望你的丈夫\N{\rEN}You don't expect your husband's
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.31,1:17:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,会做这样的事情 对吧\N{\rEN}gonna do something like that, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.96,1:17:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,反正没有人会相信的\N{\rEN}I mean, nobody would believe it, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.36,1:17:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我…然后…\N{\rEN}And then I... and then...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.80,1:17:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我想...\N{\rEN}And then I figured...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.28,1:17:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我想 如果李都清理干净了..\N{\rEN}And then I figured, if Lee was clean...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.59,1:18:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他干净的话\N{\rEN}If he was clean,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.38,1:18:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,睡前灌肠 洗个澡什么的...\N{\rEN}an enema and a bath before bed...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.25,1:18:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...那对我们大家都好\N{\rEN}...then it would be better for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.73,1:18:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,确实如此\N{\rEN}And it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.09,1:18:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我在做什么 这...\N{\rEN}I knew what I was doing, it wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.87,1:18:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这不对\N{\rEN}it wasn't quite right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.39,1:18:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的 真的\N{\rEN}I did know that. I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.79,1:18:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但你能告诉谁呢 你知道吗\N{\rEN}But who do you tell? You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.49,1:18:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我能告诉谁\N{\rEN}Who could I tell?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.01,1:18:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你只能这样了\N{\rEN}I mean, you do the best you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.63,1:18:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道当你有了孩子之后会发生什么吗\N{\rEN}You know what happens when you have children?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.85,1:18:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫看你的眼神再也不一样了\N{\rEN}Your husband never looks at you the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.73,1:18:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但当他和李上床后\N{\rEN}But after he went to bed with Lee,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.38,1:18:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他会来找我的\N{\rEN}he'd come to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.52,1:19:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他好像是卸下了一个很大的负担\N{\rEN}It was like a big burden had been lifted.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.26,1:19:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他是 他很放松\N{\rEN}He was, he was relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.31,1:19:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他抱着我的感觉真好\N{\rEN}It felt good, how he'd hold me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.70,1:19:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那时他一定是爱我的\N{\rEN}He loved me then.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.66,1:19:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他会在我耳边轻声细语然后吻我\N{\rEN}He would whisper and kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.62,1:19:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,以前也是这样…\N{\rEN}It was the way it had been before...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.63,1:19:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,…那时我们年轻 快乐 还彼此相爱\N{\rEN}...when we were young and happy and in love.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.46,1:19:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那感觉很好\N{\rEN}It felt good.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.03,1:19:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我错了吗…\N{\rEN}Is that so wrong...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.08,1:19:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,…我只是想要重温那时的感觉\N{\rEN}...to want to feel like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.47,1:19:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会明白的\N{\rEN}You wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.61,1:19:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你还年轻 你的心还没有被谁伤过\N{\rEN}You're young, you haven't had your heart broken.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.66,1:20:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我在流血 我在流血\N{\rEN}I'm bleeding! I'm bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.10,1:20:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,帮帮我 帮帮我\N{\rEN}Help me! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.75,1:20:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 帮帮我\N{\rEN}Please! Plea... Help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.58,1:20:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我在流血\N{\rEN}I'm bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.49,1:20:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 帮帮我 你们会后悔的  - 艾琳 帮帮我\N{\rEN}- Help me! You'll be sorry! - Eileen, help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.10,1:20:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我会告诉所有人你们做了什么\N{\rEN}I'll tell everyone what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.50,1:20:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 艾琳  - 叫医生\N{\rEN}- Eileen! - A doctor!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.50,1:20:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快去找医生\N{\rEN}Get a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.07,1:20:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 带我出去 - 艾琳 帮帮我\N{\rEN}- Get me out of here! - Eileen, help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.20,1:20:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我\N{\rEN}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.86,1:20:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不\N{\rEN}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.08,1:20:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEN}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.35,1:20:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不\N{\rEN}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.65,1:20:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 好了\N{\rEN}Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.10,1:21:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么开枪打她\N{\rEN}Why did you shoot her?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.72,1:21:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我很生气\N{\rEN}I was upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.90,1:21:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在该怎么办\N{\rEN}What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.87,1:21:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们带她去我家\N{\rEN}We take her to my house.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.05,1:22:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸总是会掏出枪\N{\rEN}My dad's always whipping his gun out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.18,1:22:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都知道\N{\rEN}Everyone knows it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.14,1:22:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以伪造成他在迷糊的时候开枪打中了她\N{\rEN}We can make it look like he shot her in a blackout.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.58,1:22:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是个醉酒的混蛋 对吗\N{\rEN}He's just a drunk piece of shit, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.15,1:22:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,反正他最后不是疯掉就是死掉\N{\rEN}He's gonna die anyway or go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.85,1:22:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,医生是这么说的\N{\rEN}The doctor said so.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.94,1:22:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们带她一起走吧\N{\rEN}So let's take her together and leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.07,1:22:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们可以去纽约过新年…\N{\rEN}Then we could go to New York for the New Year...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.77,1:22:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...就我们俩\N{\rEN}...just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.30,1:22:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\rEN}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.69,1:22:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的\N{\rEN}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.78,1:22:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\rEN}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.35,1:22:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEN}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.67,1:23:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你先去你父亲家\N{\rEN}You go ahead to your father's house.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.02,1:23:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里等我\N{\rEN}Wait for me there.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.24,1:23:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好 - 我会清理好里面\N{\rEN}- Yeah. - I'll clean up inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.67,1:23:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能留下任何证据\N{\rEN}We can't leave any evidence behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.93,1:23:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我等你 - 我会快点的\N{\rEN}- I'll be waiting. - I'll be quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.78,1:27:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳\N{\rEN}Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.57,1:27:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳\N{\rEN}Eileen.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.92,1:27:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,继续睡觉吧 爸爸\N{\rEN}Go back to sleep, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.97,1:27:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里\N{\rEN}Where you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.96,1:27:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是要走了\N{\rEN}I might just get on the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.49,1:28:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEN}All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.58,1:28:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\rEN}Good night.
